    <span class="rule"></span>
    <p class="t-lead t-pretty">Rethinking Society welcomes support from individuals, foundations, organisations, and ethical businesses whose work is compatible with human dignity, ecological responsibility, democratic participation, and care for the whole.</p>
    <p class="t-body t-pretty" style="margin-top: var(--sp-4);">Financial support does not determine episode topics, conclusions, or editorial positions. The independence and integrity of the work remain essential — partnerships may be quietly declined when they conflict with these values.</p>
